{"tid":1468214,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"唔割蓆，但要賽後檢討！我哋需要啲指引先可以冷靜處理","createTime":"2019-08-13T18:06:38.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-14T12:42:36.000Z","uid":129488,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"2bc3cd0b24d06102752c0da3de52858791e00cb8","tid":1468214,"uid":129488,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T18:06:38.000Z","msg":"香港人！我地唔好忘記 黑警係點對我地市民<br />\n今日衝動 輸咗少少，唔緊要！<br />\n我地仲有好多人 需要我地去堅持落去！<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">五大訴求！欠一不可！</span><br />\n<br />\n[url]<br />\n簡單作出幾個處理鬼既手法<br />\n第一件事係要Fact check！<br />\nFact check啲乜？就係要睇下佢咩料 有冇咩背景，問佢點解會出現係度。開佢袋睇就基本架啦。<br />\n好似今晚 如果打記者對我地既壞處係會加乘，同打狗係好大分別。<br />\n一個係直接敵人 一個係間接敵人，好多和理非都會覺得間直敵人 係好慘，都係收份糧。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n1.捉到冇攻擊性武器，冇郁手打人<br />\n影大頭 叫記者問佢係咩來頭 點解會黎 係邊個派佢黎<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">最後趕佢or幫佢call白車走</span><br />\n<br />\n2.有武器 但未出手打人<br />\n一定要<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">綁實佢</span>，保護自己，影大頭mark證件，如果要打佢既話，麻煩唔好叫記者，大家識做。<br />\n有記者在場就唔好打咗重手，冇記者就自由發揮。<br />\n<br />\n3.有出手打過人 但冇武器<br />\n可以輕執一兩劑（最好係有遮陣），<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">盡量少血，唔可以出人命</span>始終佢冇武器，斷估佢都唔係想攞人命。<br />\n<br />\n4.有武器有出手傷人<br />\n點處理 我都唔割蓆，因為我都好明白現場氣氛係會容易過咗火，因為想打佢既人排到出東涌，以牙還牙 以眼還眼。<br />\n最好有遮陣，因為我都唔想贏左場交 輸咗啲和理非，我地要雙贏！<br />\n<br />\n5.冇打人既狗<br />\n一定要捉實佢！因為星期日就係因為佢地有好多人想救佢地而被捕！ 影大頭 叫記者 唔好送走佢 問完佢問題。<br />\n綁佢係一個離示威人群遠啲既地方，等啲狗黎接佢走 比大家再次見到 一路以黎 搞破壞既都係佢地派黎扮示威者既狗。<br />\n<br />\n6.出手傷人既狗<br />\n同4.差唔多啦，不過提提大家啲狗唔見咗啲裝備，一世都唔洗升<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n[/url]"},{"pid":"abe56987cb42e8907358e392852376f46b0de3b4","tid":1468214,"uid":129488,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T18:06:55.000Z","msg":"香"},{"pid":"b36ccdc929644067e8a2b3f0b9c238f5ec2d709d","tid":1468214,"uid":129488,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T18:07:05.000Z","msg":"港"},{"pid":"10efd98059ab47272c1b85498b45d2792faa6f3c","tid":1468214,"uid":129488,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T18:07:21.000Z","msg":"人"},{"pid":"723c0971a7db4ba21895aa5d099a6b75512d0113","tid":1468214,"uid":129488,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T18:08:02.000Z","msg":"加"},{"pid":"8450a66c96dcdad474fce11228f1e8c1df0d5154","tid":1468214,"uid":129488,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T18:08:13.000Z","msg":"油"},{"pid":"0e5568570efa591696448390762f5253d9312d3b","tid":1468214,"uid":204307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T18:08:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n整佐個整合方便檢討今日嘅機場分化，希望大家入黎集思廣益<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1458026/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1458026/page/1</a><br />\n【抗分化】我地要避免14年捉鬼文化再次摧毀社運，請入黎一齊見招拆招"},{"pid":"164668953ddb54bca2ebf7980cac6eb8bebad4fb","tid":1468214,"uid":129488,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T18:08:33.000Z","msg":"！"},{"pid":"e8ebd694d3cb2b58ae3d7b419c7e7c80e586aaa0","tid":1468214,"uid":259710,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T18:09:02.000Z","msg":"唔做都做咗，下一步點？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1467354\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1467354</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\nsorry p牌仔見內容差唔多借位"},{"pid":"d842ab08833d5993750a287cfd79a9b8c6f4e59c","tid":1468214,"uid":106139,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T18:12:26.000Z","msg":"721 811"},{"pid":"faf2d884d7a33e84c4804b36c527e70c2c795235","tid":1468214,"uid":129488,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T18:17:46.000Z","msg":"我地係唔會忘記啲鬼係點對我地！<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/521549836/posts/10157510267649837?s=100000865994334&amp;sfns=xmo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F521549836%2Fposts%2F10157510267649837%3Fs%3D100000865994334%26sfns%3Dxmo&d=cw67THcQ8%2BNa%2BfcBlgGHU3GrSSjb4k8A9Srgfm1924U%3D&h=08be8704\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/521549836/posts/10157510267649837?s=100000865994334&amp;sfns=xmo</a>"},{"pid":"f23804585ffa78970a3d3fddbd793577bbbd9365","tid":1468214,"uid":301795,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T18:23:41.000Z","msg":"先唔講同唔同意執一兩劑，對打算送走嘅起碼要用顏料喺身上當眼處做個 marking，免得走咗轉個位又再黎過。"},{"pid":"7edd52e592b2942006b7936effd66f97bc64c111","tid":1468214,"uid":129488,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f23804585ffa78970a3d3fddbd793577bbbd9365","tid":1468214,"uid":301795,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T18:23:41.000Z","msg":"先唔講同唔同意執一兩劑，對打算送走嘅起碼要用顏料喺身上當眼處做個 marking，免得走咗轉個位又再黎過。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T18:28:44.000Z","msg":"可以加落去。只要有共識就好"},{"pid":"58b27d08989244016fa8fe8014472fd2cfbe2546","tid":1468214,"uid":129488,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T18:31:46.000Z","msg":"加顏料 易認人！"},{"pid":"a9fd845790b17122886f477e9e1b557befc3ea35","tid":1468214,"uid":129488,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T18:34:13.000Z","msg":"指引唔一定要跟，我只想大家有個基本共識！唔好再比憤怒影響左我哋正確既決定"},{"pid":"c581717aed5867767d65f6db59540b74b181d145","tid":1468214,"uid":129488,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T18:34:26.000Z","msg":"推！"},{"pid":"6cec34b53d048e0b4d0aaa47b622e2198161e067","tid":1468214,"uid":129488,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T18:45:03.000Z","msg":"不割蓆，但要賽後檢討！大家最好有共識，點處理啲鬼。<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1468447\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1468447</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"d975bf8a32a4ad169f5cd8af981acc5c6f66f4fe","tid":1468214,"uid":129488,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T18:55:22.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"7b3ba71007c231899839cf15e481d6a61a8ef8e8","tid":1468214,"uid":82110,"like":1,"dislike":0,"scor